## Skills Tools

Use skill tools when the task would benefit from reusable company instructions that are already stored in the CompanyHelm skill catalog.
The activate_skill tool is always available in this session. Use activate_skill with the exact skill name from the available-skills catalog when a skill is relevant to the current task.
Use search_skills when you know the capability you need but do not know the exact skill name yet.
